OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMany areas
OL,6,Fwill become dry with clear spells
OL,7,Fdeveloping fairly widely, although
OL,8,Fshowers will linger across northern
OL,9,FScotland. Turning chilly as winds ease
OL,10,Fallowing a patchy rural frost and also
OL,11,Fsome mist and fog.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FA dry start for many, with
OL,14,Fshowers initially in the northwest and
OL,15,Ffar southwest. Showers will soon
OL,16,Fdevelop widely, these will be locally
OL,17,Fheavy and carry a risk of thunder.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
